OpenStreetMap Data License
==========================

The file oslo_central.osm.pbf contains data extracted from OpenStreetMap
(https://www.openstreetmap.org).

This data is copyright OpenStreetMap contributors and is available under
the Open Database License (ODbL) v1.0:
https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/1-0/

The extract covers a small area of central Oslo, Norway (bbox:
10.72,59.90,10.78,59.92) and is included solely for automated testing
of the extraction pipeline.

Attribution: (c) OpenStreetMap contributors
